FBIS4-1501 "drafr083_a_94001" FBIS-AFR-94-000 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Burundi Disarmament Begins in Bujumbura; Gunfire Still Heard Disarmament Begins in Bujumbura; Gunfire Still Heard EA2804212094 Bujumbura Radio-Television Nationale du Burundi Radio in Kirundi 1700 GMT 28 Apr 94 EA2804212094 Bujumbura Radio-Television Nationale du Burundi Radio Kirundi BFN [Text] The work of disarming citizens who are in possession of illegal arms officially began today. It began in the Bujumbura suburbs of Kinama, Cibitoke, and Mutakura. We can still hear gunshots in the northern suburbs of Bujumbura town.
